227
00:17:12,770 --> 00:17:18,180
[Wonder-X should just disband already. Hasn't Wonder-X caused enough trouble? I never want to see you guys again.
Seriously, Jung Ji-eun, please just leave the group. The recent songs have been absolute trash. What kind of idol group is this even supposed to be?]

228
